|title=[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9358228.stm Stoke 2-0 Bolton]
|passage=Rory Delap's long throw-ins are a familiar '''weapon''' to the Potters' opponents but this does not make them any easier to defend against.}}
